KPI: Year Over Year Applicants 10

Applicants

Drag and Drop fields in Text Mark  (Fields;  Applicants, cc. YoY Applicants, cc. YoY Applicants Down , cc. YoY Applicants Up)

Edit as in gif



Formatting the Labels with Color, Font and Size

1  - Select each field and format it  (Details are given below the snapshot)

2  - Select Color      

3 - Select More Color     

4 - Copy and paste/type in the given color code   

5 - Click OK

Do the same for each field then   6  Click Apply to see if all of them match that in the snapshot.

If it does Click OK  7 



Format Details

# of Applicants -    Size 8  

<SUM(Applicants)>  Size  26,    #5c6068 

<AGG(cc.YoY Applicants DOWN)>  Size 9,   #59a14f 

<AGG(cc.YoY Applicants UP)>  Size 9,  #c60000

<AGG(cc.YoY Applicants)> vs PY  Size 9,  #1f77b4


Format & Deactivate Tooltip

Click Text Mark to Center,  Right click SUM(Applicants) to format, Right Click AGG(cc. YoY Applicants) to Format, Click on Tooltip to de-activate it by unchecking the boxes.
